query:
SELECT rw.id as wpId, r.userId, r.id as routeId, r.name as routeName, rw.contactName, rw.address, rw.rescheduledDate 
FROM route_waypoints rw 
JOIN routes r ON rw.routeId = r.id 
WHERE rw.rescheduledDate IS NOT NULL 
LIMIT 1;
